              A new brewery that just opened near me (actually owned by the guy that runs my LHBS) which plans to offer home brewers access to entire 50lb. sacks of grain at the &quot;bulk&quot; price.  Once that's available, I should be able to cut my per-batch cost down quite a bit if I keep a sack of 2-row and a sack of pilsner on hand.

              

              
              
