              Other things that may be resulting in lower than expected efficiency:<br /><br />1) I sparge with room temp water.  Should I be heating it up to 160 instead?<br /><br />2) I might be sparging too quickly.  I literally just pour the gallon of water out of the jug over the bag and let it drip into the bucket.

              

              
              
